bn al-Mubarak, Al-Shafi\u2019i, Ahmad, and Ishaq. They said one may\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25662,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/21\/wipe-over-socks-headgear-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":13900,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Wiping over socks and headgear in ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Bilal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, wiped over leather socks and head coverings in ablution. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 275 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Ibn Taymiyyah said, \u201cSince it is permitted for men to wipe over clothing on the head, so is it\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25538,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/04\/many-salat-one-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":13900,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Performing multiple prayers with single ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 4, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Buraydah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, prayed multiple prayers on the day of liberation with a single ablution and he wiped over his leather socks. Umar said to him, \u201cYou have done something today you have not used to do.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI have done\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":29328,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/13\/concession-urinate-standing\/","url_meta":{"origin":13900,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cleanliness: Concession to urinate while standing if needed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, came to a waste area used by people and he urinated over it while standing. I brought him water for ablution and then left him to his privacy. The Prophet called me until I was behind him and he performed\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25651,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/20\/wudu-wipe-socks-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":13900,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Wiping socks three days in travel, one day residency","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 20, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, permitted wiping over leather socks for three day and nights for the traveler, and one day and night for the resident. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 276 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim Al-Nawawi said, \u201cOur scholars\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25657,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/20\/ali-din-deen-opinion-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":13900,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Deen: Religion is based on revelation, not opinion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 20, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abd Khayr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf the religion were based upon one\u2019s opinion, one might expect the bottom of the leather sock to be wiped instead of the top. I have seen the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13900","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13900"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13900\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13900"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13900"},{"taxo